<p>Thank you for everyone who suffered through me writing this.</p>
<p>With tech work, I've been&#8230;busy, and writing this has been very important to me.</p>
<p>A great author told me recently: &quot;You've built so much of this world, but you don't live in it.&quot;</p>
<p>There was something about explosions, too.</p>
<p>Therefore, I do both. And now 3622 makes a lot more sense, I hope.</p>
<p>I wonder if anyone can identify my next article, within this one? Hmmmm?</p>

